ewline &=\sum_{p = 0}^{L}\sum_{q = 0}^{L - p}  rac{1}{n}\sum_{I = 0}^{n - 1}\omega_{n}^{I(p - i)}  rac{1}{n}\sum_{J = 0}^{n - 1}\omega_{n}^{J(q - j)}C_L^p C_{L - p}^q(k - 2)^{(L - p - q)}
